WEBVTT

00:13:28.701 --> 00:13:32.814
So emotions are localized
somewhere else entirely,

00:13:32.838 --> 00:13:34.749
memory is somewhere else.

00:13:34.773 --> 00:13:39.630
System 2, which links
self-control and intelligence --

00:13:39.654 --> 00:13:43.079
that is in the prefrontal cortex.

00:13:43.103 --> 00:13:49.896
Anyway, we can identify that locus
of being active when people reason

00:13:50.369 --> 00:13:52.618
and when they invest mental effort,

00:13:52.642 --> 00:13:55.659
whether it be in reasoning
or in self-control.

00:13:55.683 --> 00:13:59.266
CA: I mean, if you're going to write
a book about System 1, System 2,

00:13:59.290 --> 00:14:03.707
and argue for people that they should
understand their own minds better,